Alia from China Beat [puts together](http://offbeatchina.com/police-porn-
examiner-in-jiangsu-stressed-to-finish-40k-porn-dvds-in-one-month) a picture
about the work and requirement of being a police Porn examiner in China:

> To be a porn examiner, one has to be an “outstanding, well-behaved and
> highly politically-sensitive” police officer who “won’t have any problems
> after watching porn materials.”

